[23/03/2018 16:36:18] <font color="#0000ff">Suenan las campanas</font>
[23/03/2018 16:36:22] <font color="#0000ff">Graznidos</font>
[23/03/2018 16:36:31] <font color="#0000ff">Suenan las campanas</font>
[23/03/2018 16:36:40] <font color="#ffffff">Los jóvenes portugueses...</font>
